movies.title: A Hidden Life
movies.description: Franz, a simple farmer, and his family are caught off guard when the war breaks out. However, things take a turn for the worse when Franz refuses to swear an oath of allegiance to the Nazis.

movies.title: Avenger: Endgame
movies.description: After Thanos, an intergalactic warlord, disintegrates half of the universe, the Avengers must reunite and assemble again to reinvigorate their trounced allies and restore balance.

movies.title: The Death of Dick Long
movies.description: In small-town Alabama, Zeke and Earl scramble to cover up the unlikely and illegal events that led to their friend's death while trying to dodge their families, the cops and one horrified medical examiner.

movies.title: John Wick: Chapter 4
movies.description: With the price on his head ever increasing, legendary hit man John Wick takes his fight against the High Table global as he seeks out the most powerful players in the underworld, from New York to Paris to Japan to Berlin.

movies.title: Joker
movies.description: Arthur Fleck, a party clown, leads an impoverished life with his ailing mother. However, when society shuns him and brands him as a freak, he decides to embrace the life of crime and chaos.

series.title: Stranger Things
series.description: When a young boy vanishes, a small town uncovers a mystery involving secret experiments, terrifying supernatural forces and one strange little girl. Watch all you want. This nostalgic nod to '80s sci-fi and horror classics has earned dozens of Emmy nominations, including three for Outstanding Drama.

series.title: Altered Carbon - S2
series.description: After 250 years on ice, a prisoner returns to life in a new body with one chance to win his freedom: by solving a mind-bending murder.
